<p source="QINGHUA.YINGAO 2.1 (STRIP 1) LIU 2011:124 Ji Xusheng 2013: 22"><pb xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.1">惟尹旣及湯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.2">咸有一德.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.3">尹念天之敗西邑夏，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.4">曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.5">“ 夏自壅其有民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.6">亦惟厥衆,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-1a.7">彼民亡與守邑</seg></p>

<p source="QINGHUA.YINGAO 2.2 (STRIP 2) LIU 2011:124 Ji Xusheng 2013: 22"><pb xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-2a.1">厥辟作怨于民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-2a.2">民復之用離心，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-2a.3">我翦滅夏.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-2a.4">今后曷不監?”</seg></p>

<p source="QINGHUA.YINGAO 2.3 (STRIPS 2-3) LIU 2011:124 Ji Xusheng 2013: 22"><pb xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.1">摯告湯曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.2">“我克協我友，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.3">今惟民遠邦歸志. ”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.4">湯曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.5">"嗚呼！吾何作于民，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-3a.6">俾我衆勿違朕言?”</seg></p>

<p source="QINGHUA.YINGAO 2.4 (STRIPS 2-4) LIU 2011:124 JI XUSHENG 2013: 22"><pb xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a.1">摯曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a.2">“后，其賚之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a.3">其有夏之金玉、田邑,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a.4">予之吉言."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0090_tls_001-4a.5">乃致衆于亳中邑.</seg></p>

